Create a new SA named backend-team. Print out the Token for the SA in YML format.

To get Token: Kubectl get SA -o yaml under secrets: -name: <<token>> 




Get the token by running the command:   
➜ k -n neptune get secret neptune-secret-1 -o yaml and decode with -   echo 'token' | base64 -d
OR
➜ k -n neptune describe secret neptune-secret-1 - this gives the decoded value
